## #dma-cells

**Value type:** `<u32>`

The *#dma-cells* property defines the number of cells required to encode a DMA specifier for this DMA controller. Used by DMA controller nodes to indicate how many `<u32>` cells follow the phandle in `dmas` references.

```dts
/* arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/sm8550.dtsi */
gpi_dma1: dma-controller@a00000 {
    compatible = "qcom,sm8550-gpi-dma";
    #dma-cells = <3>;
};
```
